Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard stories, but I never
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.75,0:00:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,imagined it would be like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.16,0:00:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This place holds secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.50,0:00:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.26,0:00:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She only needed one interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.08,0:00:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago Quint was the billionaire
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,no one could reach, and that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.28,0:00:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,story could save her career.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.12,0:00:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So she accepted the most
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,dangerous deal of her life,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.83,0:00:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,pretending
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.36,0:00:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,to be his girlfriend for one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.84,0:00:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.64,0:00:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It was supposed to be simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.40,0:00:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Walk into the ball convinces
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.70,0:00:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,family and walk out with the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.01,0:00:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,answers she
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.52,0:00:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,needed, but when
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.64,0:00:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago's mother demanded proof of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.33,0:00:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,love in front of everyone, she
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.96,0:00:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,did exactly what she
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.88,0:00:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She kissed Jago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.32,0:00:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And that kiss, which was only
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.92,0:00:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,supposed to be a lie,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.62,0:00:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,started to feel far too real.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.73,0:00:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapter One, The Impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.45,0:00:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.11,0:00:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,His room smelled of reheated
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:00:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,coffee and old paper,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.75,0:00:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and Rowina Pike had already
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.13,0:00:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,drunk
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.39,0:00:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,three cups before nine in the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.94,0:01:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.83,0:01:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The gray light coming through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the window gave every face their
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.06,0:01:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the same shade of exhaustion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.19,0:01:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of fatigue that doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.95,0:01:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,come from one bad night's sleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.70,0:01:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but from months, piled
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.91,0:01:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,one on top of another.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.61,0:01:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She knew, hers was no different.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.99,0:01:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She held her folder against her
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.69,0:01:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,chest, and crossed the narrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.29,0:01:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,aisle between the desks,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.61,0:01:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,greeting with a Kurt Nord anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.45,0:01:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,who looked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.67,0:01:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wallace Vaughn was waiting for
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.13,0:01:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,her with his elbows planted on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.58,0:01:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the desk, glasses pushed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.75,0:01:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,to the tip of his nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.41,0:01:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The editor had a peculiar way of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.97,0:01:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,looking at people, as if he were
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.53,0:01:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,checking whether they
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.55,0:01:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,were worth their own salary.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.43,0:01:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina shut the door behind her,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.12,0:01:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,ignored the chair he didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.54,0:01:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,offer, and sat down without
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.97,0:01:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting for an invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.47,0:01:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I need the interview Pike.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.41,0:01:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wallace didn't waste time on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.02,0:01:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,introductions, and I need
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.46,0:01:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,something else too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.55,0:01:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're about to tell me you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.97,0:01:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,need a photo of Quint without
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.34,0:01:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,his jacket, I'm walking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.43,0:01:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,out of this room right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.13,0:01:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a file.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.51,0:01:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The sentence landed in the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:01:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,middle of the desk, like
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,something too heavy for the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.16,0:01:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,furniture.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.21,0:01:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina raised an eyebrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.63,0:02:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting for him to refraise to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.33,0:02:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,apologise to turn it into a
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.87,0:02:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.59,0:02:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wallace did none of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.07,0:02:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He simply laced his fingers, and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,kept looking at her, as if he
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.46,0:02:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,were collecting on an old
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.69,0:02:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Proof, he added.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That that empire is hiding
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,something it shouldn't be
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.49,0:02:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.81,0:02:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone hides something Pike.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.17,0:02:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You just need to find out what.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.07,0:02:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to get inside the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.56,0:02:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,home of the most closed off
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.94,0:02:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,family in the south.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Land the interview no one's
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.72,0:02:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,managed to land in 10 years, and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.37,0:02:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,still walk out of there with
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.81,0:02:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,compromising material.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.37,0:02:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you that your job
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.90,0:02:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,here depends on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.11,0:02:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't answer right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She sat staring at the coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,stain on the rim of his mug.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.73,0:02:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Calculating how much of next
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.24,0:02:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,month's salary was already
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,committed to rent, how much was
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,still
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.57,0:02:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,owed on her mother's bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.77,0:02:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The window behind Hollis let in
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.46,0:02:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the muffled noise of the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A horn, a quick step.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.49,0:02:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The city running nonstop while
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.97,0:02:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,she sat there deciding how far
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.45,0:02:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,she was willing to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.85,0:02:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then she nodded once, short,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,like someone signing a contract
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:02:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,they haven't yet read.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.81,0:02:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Marlow Trent intercepted her in
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the hallway with two fresh
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,coffees, and a smile that was
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.23,0:03:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,already a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.61,0:03:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Marlow was a copy editor, a
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,colleague of three years, and
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.80,0:03:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the only person in the newsroom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.57,0:03:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,who understood when Rowine
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,needed silence and when she
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,needed noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like someone who just
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.22,0:03:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,sold her soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.19,0:03:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Marlow remarked, handing over
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the hot-a-cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it for much?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It was for next month's rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.03,0:03:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Marlow laughed, a short laugh,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.88,0:03:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,cut off halfway by the awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that the joke was worth
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.27,0:03:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,more to herself than to Rowine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.63,0:03:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She leaned her shoulder against
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine as they walked down the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,hallway, and for a moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.57,0:03:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine felt like dropping
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.78,0:03:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,everything right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.89,0:03:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Walking out the front door, and
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.74,0:03:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,never coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She drank the coffee until it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,burned her tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.81,0:03:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,After noon came quickly, and
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.33,0:03:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,with it a note left at the front
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.77,0:03:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No sender, just her name on the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,front of the envelope, written
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,in black pen and handwriting
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,that wasn't a friend, slanted
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.89,0:03:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,controlled letters, each one in
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.19,0:03:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,its exact place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.87,0:03:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine had turned the envelope
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.52,0:04:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,over twice before opening it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,inside just an address and
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.51,0:04:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.13,0:04:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The office it pointed to was
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.69,0:04:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,three blocks away, in a discreet
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,building she had never noticed,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.67,0:04:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,despite having walked past it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,hundreds of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.55,0:04:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The sign at the entrance simply
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,read Ashford and Associates, in
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,letters too small to draw
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.95,0:04:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.03,0:04:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine had climbed the steps
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,with her folder still pressed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,against her chest, and greeted
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.05,0:04:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the receptionist with the name
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.31,0:04:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that was on the note.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.65,0:04:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who received her was
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.85,0:04:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,younger than she expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Tall, navy, suit, no tie, with
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.28,0:04:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,that kind of discretion only old
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.15,0:04:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,money teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.03,0:04:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The extended his hand and
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.51,0:04:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,introduced himself as Silas
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.11,0:04:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ashford, the Quint family's
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,lawyer,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.49,0:04:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,a friend of Jago's since their
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,boarding school days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.31,0:04:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The information came without
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.79,0:04:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,fanfare, the way someone hands
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,over a business card.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a seat, Miss Pike.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,His voice had the same tone as
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the handwriting on the envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be brief because the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,proposal is brief.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Quint agrees to grant a
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,two-hour interview to your
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,publication, no restrictions
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:05:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,on subject matter, except one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.63,0:05:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Silas made a minimal pause.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of pause lawyers used
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,to let the client swallow the
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,next piece of information.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.67,0:05:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,In return, you would attend the
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,family's Gallaboll in Savannah
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.15,0:05:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,as his companion on Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,One night, just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine elapsed before her brain
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,authorized her mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.03,0:05:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.15,0:05:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the word he preferred.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.99,0:05:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And what word didn't he prefer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The corner of Silas's mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.54,0:05:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,moved half a millimeter, almost
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,the beginning of a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but nothing followed through.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He slid a black envelope across
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.65,0:05:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,the desk, sealed, with her name
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.45,0:05:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,written on the front
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.61,0:05:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,in the same slanted, controlled
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,handwriting as the first note.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Letters she now recognized
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,without effort and which
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.67,0:05:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,definitely did not belong to
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Silas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The rules are in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.47,0:05:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,One read is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.81,0:05:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He expects an answer today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.73,0:05:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine looked at the black
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,envelope for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.29,0:05:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She thought about the rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She thought about the look on
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Holis's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She thought about the old
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.42,0:05:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,photograph of the reclusive
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.63,0:05:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,billionaire
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.13,0:06:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,that had circulated through the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,papers forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.61,0:06:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Always the same profile of a
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.10,0:06:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,clenched jaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Always the same gaze that didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,invite anyone to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.61,0:06:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She tucked the envelope into her
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.31,0:06:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,folder without opening it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him I'll be in Savannah on
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.19,0:06:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Silas nodded like someone who
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.48,0:06:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,already knew the answer before
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He rose, shook her hand again
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.68,0:06:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and walked her to the door with
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.61,0:06:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,practice courtesy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.31,0:06:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Before closing the handle, he
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,said almost without voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.35,0:06:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not what the press writes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.68,0:06:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine didn't ask what he meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.31,0:06:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She preferred not to know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Marlo was waiting for her on the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.61,0:06:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,street with a cigarette that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.77,0:06:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,pretended to be lit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.09,0:06:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of theatre she used as
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.64,0:06:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,an excuse to loiter on corners.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.77,0:06:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine handed over the black
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.99,0:06:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,envelope without ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend turned the object over
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,in her hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,studied the seal with more
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,attention than necessary, and
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.08,0:06:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,gave it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't open it now, Marlo said,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.81,0:06:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,open it on the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.21,0:06:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's prettier that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.49,0:06:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.31,0:06:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to be someone else's
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,story or make history?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.75,0:06:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's the second, you open it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:06:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,on the train alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and you cry if you need to cry
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,without anyone seeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.45,0:07:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the least you deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.29,0:07:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine laughed and the laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,pulled some of the weight off
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She rested her forehead on
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.40,0:07:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Marlo's shoulder for a short
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,second.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.55,0:07:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Just enough to remember she
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,still had a friend in that grey
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,city,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.01,0:07:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and then she went home to pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The station was too crowded for
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.44,0:07:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,her taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.51,0:07:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine had dragged her luggage
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,between hurried bodies,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,bought a sandwich she wasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,going to eat,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.43,0:07:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and settled by the window of the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The seats smelled of dust and
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,warm synthetic leather.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.89,0:07:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That smell of a place where many
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,people have passed without
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,leaving a trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.75,0:07:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She sat staring at the tracks
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.25,0:07:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.17,0:07:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,before taking the black envelope
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.61,0:07:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,out of the inner pocket of her
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.53,0:07:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The seal gave way with a dry
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside, three folded sheets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.83,0:07:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The first two carried
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,instructions written with almost
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,legal precision.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.85,0:07:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Times, names she should
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,memorize,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.45,0:07:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,clothes that would be delivered
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,to the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What to say if anyone asked how
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.92,0:07:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,long they had known each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.93,0:07:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine erred them with the same
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.38,0:07:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,attention she gave to story
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:07:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,contracts,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.81,0:08:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,mentally noting every detail,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,every gap between the lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.59,0:08:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The third sheet was smaller, a
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,single line written by hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.78,0:08:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,unsigned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.99,0:08:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't smile at anyone like you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Only smile when I'm looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.07,0:08:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She read it three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She put it away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.05,0:08:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She looked out the window as the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.56,0:08:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,train picked up speed and the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,city opened into suburb,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.05,0:08:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,then countryside,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.79,0:08:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,then nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.89,0:08:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And she couldn't decide whether
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.62,0:08:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,that was an order, a warning, or
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.41,0:08:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.57,0:08:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The train arrived in Savannah in
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.91,0:08:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the late afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The air changed before she even
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.75,0:08:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,stepped onto the platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Warmer, denser,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.39,0:08:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,laid in with a sweet perfume she
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn't yet name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.47,0:08:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Magnolia maybe, or something
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.23,0:08:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that grew near water.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine across the station with
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.42,0:08:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,her folder under her arm,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.09,0:08:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,looking for the driver who would
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,be waiting with her name on a
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.77,0:08:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.99,0:08:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She found the dark car outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,a man in a suit opening the back
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,door without ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Before getting in, she looked
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.45,0:08:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,one last time at the city's
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,skyline and saw in the distance,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the high roof of the quint
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,mansion cut against the sky that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.13,0:09:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,was beginning to turn orange.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.07,0:09:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Too big, too old, the kind of
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.05,0:09:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,house that doesn't invite you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.03,0:09:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.49,0:09:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It absorbs you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.97,0:09:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine sat on the leather seat,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,rested her head against the cold
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,glass,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and pressed the black envelope
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.57,0:09:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,against her lap,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.33,0:09:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,like someone clutching a
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,boarding pass to another
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.97,0:09:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,country.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.85,0:09:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She took the sheet out one more
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Only smile when I'm looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She re-read it, folded it, put
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.28,0:09:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.35,0:09:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The car started up, and the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,streets of Savannah began to
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.55,0:09:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,pass by outside like a borrowed
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,set,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.89,0:09:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,with the moss heavy trees and
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.33,0:09:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the old houses that each guarded
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.92,0:09:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,their own version of a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.83,0:09:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And for the first time since
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.04,0:09:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Holly's Vaughn had uttered the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,word,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.77,0:09:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,file, Rowine a pike wondered,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,whether she could go home as the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.34,0:09:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,same person who had boarded the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,train.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The chapter 2, a three second
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.28,0:09:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hotel suite was bigger than her
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.00,0:09:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,entire apartment,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,with a soft smell of jasmine
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that seemed built into the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.05,0:09:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:09:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine looked at herself in the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.44,0:10:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,oval mirror for a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.13,0:10:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,adjusting the wine-colored silk
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.64,0:10:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,dress they had left hanging
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,behind the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.13,0:10:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The fabric fell effortlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of piece that only
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,existed when someone paid for it
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,without thinking twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.01,0:10:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The driver knocked at the door
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.55,0:10:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,at the exact time indicated in
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.08,0:10:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.35,0:10:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine went down, crossed the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,lobby under stairs she pretended
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,not to notice,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and found the car waiting at the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,curb.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.83,0:10:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The back door opened before she
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,touched the handle,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and the first thing she saw
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.76,0:10:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,inside was the impeccable crease
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,of dark trousers,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,running down to a pair of
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.95,0:10:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,polished black shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.49,0:10:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago Quint was seated on the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.74,0:10:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,other side of the seat,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,with one knee slightly apart
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,from the other, hands resting on
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.46,0:10:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,his own thighs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't stand, didn't extend
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.52,0:10:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.61,0:10:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He merely tilted his chin and
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,inch toward the empty spot
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.48,0:10:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,beside him,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.25,0:10:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and waited.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.49,0:10:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine got in, adjusted her
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,skirt with a quick gesture,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.01,0:10:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and shut the door with more
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.24,0:10:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,force than necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.77,0:10:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.77,0:10:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,She saw that he noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.51,0:10:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither of them commented.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:10:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening Miss Pike.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.57,0:11:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,His voice was lower than she had
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.02,0:11:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,imagined from any interview
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,she'd ever read.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A voice that didn't rise because
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,it didn't need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine returned her face and
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,looked at him full on for the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and had the displeasure of
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.07,0:11:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,confirming that the portraits
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.39,0:11:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,published over the years did
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.67,0:11:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,him no justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.01,0:11:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,In person, he was a sculpture of
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.98,0:11:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,a straight jaw,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.31,0:11:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,dark hair combed back with
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.63,0:11:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,calculated carelessness,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.27,0:11:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and eyes that decided the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.65,0:11:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,temperature of the room before
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.30,0:11:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,saying anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening Mr. Quint.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.55,0:11:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Rowine will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He nodded almost imperceptibly,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.32,0:11:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the car started up,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.55,0:11:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and for a while the two of them
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.30,0:11:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,sat in silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine noticed his hands resting
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,on his knees,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.37,0:11:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,long fingers, a silver watch
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.06,0:11:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,with no visible brand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.87,0:11:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She also noticed that the seat
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.29,0:11:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,between them held a thin leather
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,folder,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,closed, with one corner leaning
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.15,0:11:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,against the glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.69,0:11:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Details.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,She collected details.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.51,0:11:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are the rules clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He asked without turning his
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.01,0:11:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.75,0:11:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:11:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Any questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:11:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,One.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:11:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine awaited until he finally
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.13,0:12:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,turned his gaze to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How long do you intend for this
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.87,0:12:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,night to last?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as necessary, that's not
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.93,0:12:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only one I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.37,0:12:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He looked forward again and
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.68,0:12:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine accepted defeat in that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.13,0:12:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,round without arguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.69,0:12:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She kept watching his profile
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,against the dark window.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.81,0:12:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The hard line of his jaw, the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.36,0:12:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,way his thumb pressed against
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.90,0:12:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,his own knee in a steady rhythm,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.99,0:12:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,like someone counting something
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,inside himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.61,0:12:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She stored the gesture in her
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.14,0:12:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,memory, and said nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.91,0:12:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The Quint mentioned appeared at
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.40,0:12:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the end of the avenue of tall
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.80,0:12:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,trees,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.09,0:12:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,lit from outside like a theatre
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.16,0:12:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,set.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine drew a deep breath before
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.37,0:12:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the car stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.71,0:12:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago got out first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Went around the vehicle and
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,opened her door with a courtesy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that sounded more rehearsed
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.27,0:12:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,than sincere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.45,0:12:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He offered his arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.89,0:12:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,His palm brushed briefly against
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,her hand as he helped her
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.94,0:12:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,position herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.23,0:12:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and the temperature changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.01,0:12:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't smile at anyone like you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.59,0:12:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He murmured.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.29,0:12:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Barely moving his lips as they
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.99,0:12:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,climb the steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.31,0:12:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You already warned me in
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.47,0:12:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.85,0:12:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm reinforcing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.89,0:13:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The main hall swallowed them the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.23,0:13:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,moment the door opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.81,0:13:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine smelled it before she saw
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Magnolia and old money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly as Silas had said in the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.09,0:13:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,instruction note.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The white walls rose high to a
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.09,0:13:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,ceiling of worked stucco,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.97,0:13:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and everywhere there were
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.05,0:13:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,antique chandeliers spreading a
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.39,0:13:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,honey-colored light over the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.53,0:13:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Long dresses, emerald chocas,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.87,0:13:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,men in black tuxedoes,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.81,0:13:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,greeting each other without
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.89,0:13:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,enthusiasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.89,0:13:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago introduced her to three
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,couples in a row,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,always with the same assembled
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My companion for the evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.25,0:13:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine a pike.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No complicated surnames.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.43,0:13:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No deer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.59,0:13:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine a smile in just the right
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Answered questions in just the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.51,0:13:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,right measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And noticed everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She noticed that he avoided the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.68,0:13:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,terrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Twice a waiter passed offering
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to take guests out to the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.25,0:13:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,outdoor area.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.31,0:13:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And both times Jago declined,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.77,0:13:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,with a minimal gesture of his
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,chin,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.49,0:13:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,without even looking at the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.64,0:13:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,glass door.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.57,0:13:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She also noticed that his gaze
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.55,0:13:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,had one point,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.85,0:14:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,tripped over an empty chair near
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.21,0:14:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A chair upholstered in dark
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.49,0:14:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,green velvet,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.63,0:14:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,slightly set apart from the rest
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.81,0:14:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,of the arrangement,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,as if it belonged to someone who
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.59,0:14:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,used to sit there and hadn't
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.88,0:14:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,arrived yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.61,0:14:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He looked away quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.17,0:14:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine a stored it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What an unlikely evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.07,0:14:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The voice came from behind her
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,sweetest syrup heated too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.65,0:14:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine a turned and found a
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.95,0:14:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,woman with red hair pinned in a
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.45,0:14:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,low
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,one, an emerald green dress, a
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,smile that didn't reach her
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.54,0:14:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.45,0:14:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago stiffened beside her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.39,0:14:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Odeit, he greeted her without
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.03,0:14:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Odeit Mashaan extended her hand
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.48,0:14:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,to Rowine,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.45,0:14:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,palm down the gesture of someone
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.42,0:14:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,expecting reverence,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.15,0:14:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and the companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.75,0:14:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you do dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I write.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.31,0:14:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A. Odeit seemed to decide
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.85,0:14:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,something in silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How brave of him to bring you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.29,0:14:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Brave of me to agree to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Odeit laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.29,0:14:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A short note that contained
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.44,0:14:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing of laughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.75,0:14:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then she moved off with a wave
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.06,0:14:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,of her fingers,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:14:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,leaving behind a trail of
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.63,0:14:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,expensive perfume.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.11,0:15:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago rested his hand at the
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,small of Rowine's back
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,for just a second, a gesture of
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.31,0:15:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,ownership that wasn't a
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.89,0:15:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,affection.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.73,0:15:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he withdrew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't need to provoke her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.75,0:15:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He remarked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.65,0:15:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Low.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.47,0:15:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I did, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.09,0:15:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.11,0:15:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But the corner of his mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.19,0:15:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,moved a millimeter,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.95,0:15:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and Rowine arrested it as if it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,were the headline of the month.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a smile yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.51,0:15:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.95,0:15:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The silence in the hall changed
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.79,0:15:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,texture.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.79,0:15:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Before she understood why.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It was as if the air had drawn
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.11,0:15:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,back a few inches,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and everybody there in unison
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.05,0:15:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,had turned their heads in the
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.57,0:15:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,same direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.09,0:15:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine followed the others gaze,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and saw Udora quint entering
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.67,0:15:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,through the main door.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The matriarch didn't need to
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,announce herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.41,0:15:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The long black dress, a pearl
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,necklace that fell to the middle
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,of her chest,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.47,0:15:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,gray hair pinned with a rigidity
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.86,0:15:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that allowed no discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She crossed the hall without
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.71,0:15:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,greeting anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.79,0:15:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and stopped before her son and
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,his companion,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,with the expression of someone
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.59,0:15:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,appraising merchandise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening, mother, said Jago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.71,0:16:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Udora didn't answer her son.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She turned her pale eyes to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.67,0:16:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and examined her from shoes to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,hairstyle with a surgical calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Then she stepped half a step
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,closer,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.91,0:16:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and the voice that came out of
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.54,0:16:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,her was low,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.33,0:16:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but sharp enough to cut the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.59,0:16:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,entire hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.67,0:16:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see love here, my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The silence closed around the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,three of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.49,0:16:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine felt Jago's body
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.85,0:16:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,stiffened beside her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,His shoulders rising half an
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.76,0:16:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,inch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Udora stayed put, chin raised
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.33,0:16:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.41,0:16:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Proof said the matriarch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.33,0:16:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's true, prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.27,0:16:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The entire hall turned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.07,0:16:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Heads lifted from champagne
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.38,0:16:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,glasses,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,conversation ceased.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.79,0:16:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Waiters stopped where they
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,stood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.19,0:16:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine felt the weight of the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.70,0:16:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,whole hall falling on her
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.01,0:16:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and Jago at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.89,0:16:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He locked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She saw that he locked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.41,0:16:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,His thumb stopped counting on
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,his own hip,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,his jaw hardened,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and for a whole second, no
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,decision came out of his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.81,0:16:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine had decided for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.15,0:16:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She raised her hand took his
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.55,0:16:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,face by the side and pulled.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,His mouth met hers with a
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.59,0:17:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,hesitation of someone who hadn't
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.15,0:17:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,rehearsed this scene,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.51,0:17:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and for an instant, Rowine
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,thought he wouldn't respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.85,0:17:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Then his breath faltered.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She felt the falter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,felt the air caught halfway up
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.53,0:17:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,his chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.43,0:17:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,felt his hand rise by reflex to
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,her back and settle between her
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulder blades,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,with a pressure that didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.09,0:17:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,belong to the charade.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The kiss was supposed to last a
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,second.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.03,0:17:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It lasted three.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine lost count somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.07,0:17:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,between the moment he tilted his
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.52,0:17:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,head a little to the side,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and the moment she herself
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.54,0:17:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,forgot there was a hall around
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.14,0:17:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When they pulled apart, she
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,opened her eyes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He took half a second longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.23,0:17:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And what Rowine saw on his face
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,when he finally looked back,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.77,0:17:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,was the same thing she felt
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.17,0:17:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.05,0:17:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and which she wasn't prepared to
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,name yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.39,0:17:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You'daw a stepped back half a
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.94,0:17:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,step.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.57,0:17:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She adjusted her pearl necklace
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.08,0:17:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,with a calculated carelessness,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and the corner of her mouth drew
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,a line that wasn't a smile but
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.26,0:17:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,pretended to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.21,0:17:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:17:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mermaid the matriarch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:17:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope to see you again many
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:17:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,times.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.65,0:17:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Many.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She turned on her heels and
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.75,0:18:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,moved off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.57,0:18:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The hall little by little began
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.11,0:18:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,to breathe again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.63,0:18:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Conversations returned like a
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.19,0:18:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,discrete murmur.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Waiters moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.57,0:18:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone laughed in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.89,0:18:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,at something that wasn't funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.83,0:18:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine kept looking at Jago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.75,0:18:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,His hand was still on her back
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.29,0:18:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,forgotten there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In no hurry to leave, he took
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.01,0:18:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,his time pulling it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.83,0:18:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When he did, his fingers pass
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.42,0:18:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly over the silk of the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,dress,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,like someone memorizing a path
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.91,0:18:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,they might need to retrace
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.26,0:18:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Across the hall, Odec Marchong
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.24,0:18:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,watched them with a glass in her
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.70,0:18:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and her smile was now a
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.41,0:18:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,different one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.11,0:18:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine arrested it, stored it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She already knew, without
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.29,0:18:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,needing a warning,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.71,0:18:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,that that woman would want
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.95,0:18:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,payback.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.73,0:18:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago leaned in very slightly,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.44,0:18:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and spoke close to her ear so
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.16,0:18:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,low that
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.63,0:18:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,only she could hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You owe me an explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.71,0:18:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,For the kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.95,0:18:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,For the length of the kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine didn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.07,0:18:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't know the answer yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.65,0:18:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She took the glass away to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:18:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,drank a sip she didn't even feel
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:18:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,go down,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.11,0:18:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and looked again at the empty
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.42,0:19:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,chair near the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone, at some point, had sat
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.11,0:19:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who now was no longer
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,there,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and Rowine a pike, who had
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,collected details since
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.27,0:19:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,childhood,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.47,0:19:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,understood that the most
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.56,0:19:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,important story of that night,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,had nothing to do with the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.57,0:19:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,reason Hollis Vaughan had sent
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.06,0:19:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,her there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.41,0:19:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapter 3, Coffee with No
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Recorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.17,0:19:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The morning after the ball
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.27,0:19:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,arrived without ceremony,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.93,0:19:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the Savannah Sun came through
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.20,0:19:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the gaps in the curtain of the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.51,0:19:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,guest room
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.95,0:19:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,at the quint mansion with an
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.69,0:19:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,almost impolite insistence,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.77,0:19:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and Rowine applied open her eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.63,0:19:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,before she remembered exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.32,0:19:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,where she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.35,0:19:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It took a whole instant for the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.00,0:19:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,high ceiling, the carved
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,footboard,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and the thick silence of the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.59,0:19:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,house to organize themselves in
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.11,0:19:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,her head.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.83,0:19:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Only then did the kiss come
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It came back first through her
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.53,0:19:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,lip.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.19,0:19:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Then through the nape of her
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,neck,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.05,0:19:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,then through her stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.35,0:19:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Three seconds that now carried
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the weight of biography.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.47,0:19:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She sat on the edge of the bed
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.77,0:19:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and looked at her own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.99,0:19:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They were cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.77,0:20:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone had left a coffee tray
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,on the sideboard beside the
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.27,0:20:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,door,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.93,0:20:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,during the night probably,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.25,0:20:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,because the cup was no longer
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.73,0:20:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,steaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.75,0:20:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Beside it a short note, written
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.49,0:20:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,by hand in a hand writing she
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,recognized at once,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.65,0:20:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,garden, whenever you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.59,0:20:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Jay Rowine re-read the note
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.03,0:20:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,twice just to prove to herself
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.63,0:20:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that it hadn't unsettled her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.37,0:20:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.45,0:20:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The garden was at the back of
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.97,0:20:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the house, far from the main
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.43,0:20:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She noticed that as a small
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.52,0:20:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,pay-lide housekeeper,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.61,0:20:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,let her down a corridor of
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,portraits.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.29,0:20:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The woman introduced herself as
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Nive,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.75,0:20:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,lightly squeezed Rowine's arm
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.35,0:20:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and said in an accent from rural
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.11,0:20:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Georgia,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.07,0:20:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that Mr. Jago was already
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.27,0:20:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There was warmth in her voice
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.58,0:20:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but also scrutiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine smiled with her mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.72,0:20:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,closed and asked nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago Quint was standing near an
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.10,0:20:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,old rose bush with his back to
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.56,0:20:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,White shirt sleeves folded to
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.02,0:20:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the elbow,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.25,0:20:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,hair still wet from his shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He turned when he heard the
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,gravel and for a second,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.91,0:20:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,just one, his eyes met hers
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,unguarded,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.95,0:20:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,without their usual controlled
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.60,0:20:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,gleam.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.47,0:21:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then his jaw firmed up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.55,0:21:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.67,0:21:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,As much as I could, she
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.85,0:21:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,answered,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.83,0:21:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the house makes noises.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.43,0:21:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It does. He pointed with his
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,chin toward a cast iron bench.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.33,0:21:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.25,0:21:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to work out what comes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.93,0:21:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,next.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.77,0:21:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina obeyed, but chose to sit
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.62,0:21:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,in profile knees turned outward.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A small defense he noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.97,0:21:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He said nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the interview, Jago
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.67,0:21:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,began,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.57,0:21:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,his voice low and chosen word by
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.70,0:21:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,word.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.53,0:21:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's still standing,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but last night raised an issue I
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.48,0:21:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't foresee.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.73,0:21:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother didn't believe it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.00,0:21:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,until the kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.17,0:21:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she believed it afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.97,0:21:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If you disappear tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,she'll get suspicious again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.39,0:21:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll have three candidates
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.78,0:21:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,on the table by Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.25,0:21:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're asking me for more days.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.13,0:21:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking for weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.85,0:21:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina swallowed the small shock
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.36,0:21:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and breathed through her mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.79,0:21:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,before answering.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.59,0:21:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Weeks of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.53,0:21:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Appearances.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.63,0:21:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A dinner here and event there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.35,0:21:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough for Savannah to believe
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.71,0:21:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you're the woman who finally got
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.16,0:21:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,into this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.13,0:21:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He paused.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.25,0:21:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Same payment, same interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.25,0:22:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a longer timeline.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.73,0:22:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There was logic in the proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.55,0:22:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And there was a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.75,0:22:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She knew both.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.91,0:22:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.41,0:22:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You get the interview anyway, he
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.91,0:22:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,said without hesitating.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.61,0:22:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We agreed on something and I
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.08,0:22:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,don't undo what's agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.99,0:22:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That was what disarmed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.59,0:22:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.09,0:22:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The resolution of the proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.27,0:22:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina bit the inside of her
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.57,0:22:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,cheek.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.29,0:22:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Looked at the nearest rose,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.59,0:22:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,counted to three and said yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.51,0:22:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.65,0:22:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He just nodded slightly, like
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.27,0:22:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,someone closing a clause.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.17,0:22:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But when she stood up to go back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.68,0:22:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,into the house,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.65,0:22:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,his hand brushed her back for
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.23,0:22:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,half a second, had a spot below
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.92,0:22:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,her shoulder blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.43,0:22:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And lingered an instant longer
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.88,0:22:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,than any contract required.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.61,0:22:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She stored the gesture alongside
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.17,0:22:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the others she was already
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.43,0:22:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,collecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.97,0:22:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The following weeks arrived
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.84,0:22:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly and without a truce.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.21,0:22:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina began to split herself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.55,0:22:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,between the newsroom
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.47,0:22:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,where Marlo covered her shifts
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.08,0:22:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,with increasingly irritated
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.53,0:22:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,humour
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.85,0:22:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and the streets of Savannah,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.25,0:22:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,where she learned there were
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.66,0:22:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,neighborhoods where the air
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.01,0:22:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,smelled of wet jasmine and
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.50,0:23:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,others where it only smelled of
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.27,0:23:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,hoarded money.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.51,0:23:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago always sent for her at the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.15,0:23:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,station with the same driver and
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.85,0:23:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,always in the same car.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.39,0:23:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He waited for her inside in the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.27,0:23:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,back seat,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.25,0:23:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulder leaning against the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,opposite door.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.05,0:23:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,One Tuesday, he took her to an
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.81,0:23:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,antique's fair under the oaks of
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.69,0:23:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the old square.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.11,0:23:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina stopped in front of a
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.35,0:23:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,tray of loose pendants
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.33,0:23:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and picked up one shaped like a
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.29,0:23:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,crooked owl, half green with
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.06,0:23:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,age,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.69,0:23:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,set with ridiculous red stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.01,0:23:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ugly, she said, smiling at
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.77,0:23:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the object as if it were an
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.31,0:23:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,accomplice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.43,0:23:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It is, Jago agreed, she put the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.42,0:23:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,pendant back on the tray.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.37,0:23:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't ask for it, didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.94,0:23:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,haggle, didn't look at it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.21,0:23:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Half an hour later, when they
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.59,0:23:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,were heading back to the car,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.97,0:23:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,he passed the dark velvet box
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.68,0:23:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,into her hand without any
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.16,0:23:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.63,0:23:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and Rowina stood in the middle
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.39,0:23:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,of the sidewalk, holding the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.03,0:23:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,crooked owl
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.67,0:23:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,as if it were a live animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.85,0:23:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't haggle, she remarked.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.01,0:23:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he opened the car door for
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.02,0:23:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.47,0:23:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew what it was worth to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.17,0:23:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It was that day that Rowina
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.44,0:23:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't turn on the recorder for
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.90,0:23:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the entire afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.43,0:24:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She sat with Jago in his office
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.02,0:24:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,on the 13th floor of a glass
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.46,0:24:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,building in downtown Savannah
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.95,0:24:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and they talked about things no
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.94,0:24:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,interview called for.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.29,0:24:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A cousin he had never saw, a
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.18,0:24:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,book she had read 12 times in
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.14,0:24:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,her teens,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.37,0:24:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the specific smell of the coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.76,0:24:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,her mother used to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.17,0:24:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago poured her coffee that
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.69,0:24:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,afternoon in a way she hadn't
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.31,0:24:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,taught him,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.11,0:24:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,half a spoon of sugar, a splash
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.21,0:24:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,of milk, very hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.91,0:24:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina looked at the cup, looked
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.84,0:24:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,at him, and didn't ask how he
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.59,0:24:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.31,0:24:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Nieve let the answer slip a week
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.05,0:24:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,later, in the mansions kitchen,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.29,0:24:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,while drying a crystal glass
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.65,0:24:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,with the attention of someone
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.05,0:24:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,handling something bigger than a
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.60,0:24:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.89,0:24:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been sleeping better since
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.49,0:24:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,you've been coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.97,0:24:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The housekeeper didn't look at
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.45,0:24:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina as she said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.75,0:24:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a compliment, it's an
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.41,0:24:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,observation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.99,0:24:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina laughed softly without
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.67,0:24:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,breath to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.09,0:24:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to know something
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.54,0:24:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.11,0:24:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nieve continued, putting the
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.69,0:24:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,glass away.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.75,0:24:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time since
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.10,0:24:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,anyone asked him how his day
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.51,0:24:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,was.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.03,0:24:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He would be grateful, even if he
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.71,0:25:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't know how to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.59,0:25:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina's hand trembled slightly
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.07,0:25:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,on the handle of her mug.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.57,0:25:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,She set the mug down on the
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.87,0:25:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,marble with doubled care.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.07,0:25:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The charity event took place on
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.83,0:25:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,a Thursday.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.93,0:25:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an auction in aid of a
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.47,0:25:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,children's hospital in a vaulted
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.16,0:25:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,ceiling tall,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.13,0:25:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,where the candleabras seemed too
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.76,0:25:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,heavy for the wire that held
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.19,0:25:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.73,0:25:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina wore a dark green dress
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.18,0:25:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,borrowed from Marlo's sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.05,0:25:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and Jago appeared at her side at
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.66,0:25:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the entrance, as if he'd matched
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.26,0:25:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the exact time to his own watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.41,0:25:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Odez Masha'a arrived 20 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.37,0:25:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,later.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.15,0:25:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina saw her approach from the
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.51,0:25:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,other side of the hall,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.73,0:25:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,greeting people with thin
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.18,0:25:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,kisses, a champagne coloured
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.80,0:25:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,dress moving like liquid.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.25,0:25:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Odez stopped in front of Rowina,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.18,0:25:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,looked her up and down with a
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.92,0:25:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,smile too polite to be polite,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.21,0:25:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and said in a tone that carried
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.62,0:25:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,through the three nearest
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.75,0:25:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,people,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.55,0:25:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you hold up well dear. A
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.80,0:25:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,borrowed dress in a hall of this
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.47,0:25:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,caliber isn't for just anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.45,0:25:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope the night is kind to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.25,0:25:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The air in the hall became
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.70,0:25:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,specific.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.71,0:25:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Two women near the buffet
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.93,0:25:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,stopped chewing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.45,0:25:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina felt the blood rise up
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.00,0:25:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,her neck and choose between
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.44,0:26:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,turning into fury
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.35,0:26:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and turning into dignity.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.99,0:26:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Before she could decide, Jago's
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.07,0:26:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,hand touched the small of her
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.01,0:26:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,back,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.77,0:26:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,firm, without theatrical
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.38,0:26:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,possession, just presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.71,0:26:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and he took half a step forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.34,0:26:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulder pressed against hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.31,0:26:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Odez, he said, and his voice was
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.38,0:26:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,no longer lower than usual,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.71,0:26:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,only stripped of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.03,0:26:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,amiable. If you have any doubts
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.66,0:26:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,about the woman I came with,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.37,0:26:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,put those doubts to me directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.08,0:26:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina owes you no explanation
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.68,0:26:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,about where she buys any dress,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.33,0:26:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,neither do you. Odez parted her
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.40,0:26:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,lips, and something inside her
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.41,0:26:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,smile gave way for half a
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.08,0:26:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,second,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.05,0:26:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,before recomposing. Now touch
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.91,0:26:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago, it was a compliment. It
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.76,0:26:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,wasn't. He didn't raise his
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.49,0:26:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,tone,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.09,0:26:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,he didn't need to. Two people
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.84,0:26:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,nearby rediscovered a sudden
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.53,0:26:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,fascination with their own
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.11,0:26:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,shoes. Odez
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.77,0:26:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,nodded, murmured a phrase about
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.70,0:26:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,finding a friend and withdrew.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.57,0:26:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago didn't move his hand
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.13,0:26:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,from Rowina's back for a few
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.74,0:26:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,more seconds, and in those
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.23,0:26:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,seconds she felt everything. His
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.06,0:26:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,thumb
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.35,0:26:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,resting exactly on the seam of
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.22,0:27:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,her dress, the heat of his palm,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.22,0:27:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the silent weight of being
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.84,0:27:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,chosen
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.21,0:27:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,there before an entire room.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.98,0:27:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,When he moved his hand away it
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.89,0:27:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,was slow. Rowina drew a breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.21,0:27:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't need to. I did
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.80,0:27:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,actually, he answered, without
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.70,0:27:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,looking at her. She knew what
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.54,0:27:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,she was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.91,0:27:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest of the night passed in
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.71,0:27:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,waves. Rowina won a small lot
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.39,0:27:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,with the money she had, a pair
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.13,0:27:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,of glass
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.59,0:27:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,earrings no one wanted. Jago won
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.67,0:27:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing. He just watched her
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.50,0:27:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,from afar,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.15,0:27:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,from across the hall, and every
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.10,0:27:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,time she raised her eyes, he was
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.12,0:27:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,already looking. They returned
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.01,0:27:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,to the mansion around midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.59,0:27:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She went up to the guest room
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.07,0:27:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and stood for a long time in
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.50,0:27:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,front
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.75,0:27:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,of the open suitcase on the
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.52,0:27:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,floor, at the bottom of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.30,0:27:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,under two folded blouses and a
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.27,0:27:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,pair of
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.73,0:27:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,old shoes was the file. Brown,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.14,0:27:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,no label, tied with a rubber
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.38,0:27:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,band, Rowina pulled it into her
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.87,0:27:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,lap,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.57,0:27:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,sat on the rug and stayed
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.95,0:27:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,looking. She didn't open it. She
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.72,0:27:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,ran her thumb along the edge,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.33,0:27:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,drew a deep breath, and returned
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.22,0:27:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the file to the bottom of the
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.93,0:28:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,suitcase. She folded the
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.35,0:28:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,blouses over it with exaggerated
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.13,0:28:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,care, as if covering it were
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.70,0:28:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,enough to undo what laberneth.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.87,0:28:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Her phone on the nightstand
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.73,0:28:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,vibrated. Rowina glanced
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.38,0:28:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,sideways. A missed call. Then
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.38,0:28:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,another.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.35,0:28:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Then a third one she watched
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.78,0:28:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,arrive. Pollis Vaughan's name
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.26,0:28:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,blinking on the screen like a
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.75,0:28:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,silent alarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.77,0:28:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She let it ring until it
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.98,0:28:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,stopped. She kept looking at the
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.59,0:28:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,phone until the light went out.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.15,0:28:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,When she lowered her head again,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.47,0:28:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the phone vibrated a fourth
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.43,0:28:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,time. A fifth. Rowina closed her
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.75,0:28:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.61,0:28:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Across the corridor, someone
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.51,0:28:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,walked slowly. Bear feet on the
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.62,0:28:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,wood. She knew who steps they
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.59,0:28:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,were,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.13,0:28:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and she didn't open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.22,0:28:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The phone kept. Chapter 4 The
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.31,0:28:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,File She Wouldn't Open.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.33,0:28:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,ringing. Pollis Vaughan's fifth
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.34,0:28:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,call came just after dawn, and
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.28,0:28:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,this time, Rowina answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.03,0:28:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She was sitting on the floor of
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.71,0:28:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the guest room, still in the
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.23,0:28:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,wrinkled green dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.77,0:28:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The glass earrings in her lap,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.43,0:28:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the phone trembling in her hand
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.16,0:28:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,for the sixth time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.69,0:29:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The rug beneath her smelled of
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.33,0:29:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,old lavender, the kind of
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.70,0:29:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,lavender that isn't perfume.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.87,0:29:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time. You vanished, said
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.73,0:29:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hollis without a greeting. His
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.65,0:29:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,voice had that measured calm
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.44,0:29:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that preceded
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.27,0:29:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,firings. I haven't heard your
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.99,0:29:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,voice in three weeks. Don't give
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.89,0:29:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,me behind schedule. It's behind
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.73,0:29:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,schedule. That's not the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.77,0:29:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The point is the material. Where
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.89,0:29:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,is it? I'm working. You're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.43,0:29:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina closed her eyes and
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.74,0:29:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,rested her forehead on her knee.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.36,0:29:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The knee was cold through the
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.82,0:29:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,wrinkled fabric.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.13,0:29:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Outside the garden hadn't quite
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.88,0:29:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,woken up yet. A shallow grey
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.46,0:29:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,light spread across the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.63,0:29:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,as if the day was still
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.09,0:29:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,convincing itself to arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.87,0:29:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Pollis. Rowina. He drew a deep
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.78,0:29:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,breath on
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.35,0:29:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the other end of the line. I
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.92,0:29:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,backed you. I bought the ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.71,0:29:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Pade for the hotel the first
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.28,0:29:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,weekend,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.73,0:29:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,kept your shift going with Marlo
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.45,0:29:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,covering three straight shifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.11,0:29:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a benefactor. I'm an
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.61,0:29:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,editor.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.57,0:29:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And an editor needs to deliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.09,0:29:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Either you send me something by
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.60,0:29:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Monday night or I'll have to
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.97,0:29:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,make a decision neither of us
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.83,0:29:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,once. She didn't answer right
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.70,0:30:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,away. Outside, a bird insisted
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.62,0:30:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,on the
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.01,0:30:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,same short note near the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.80,0:30:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And Rowina caught herself
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.19,0:30:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,thinking about how Jago used to
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.92,0:30:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,be late
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.31,0:30:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,with the coffee whenever there
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.91,0:30:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,was a bird nearby. He'd stand
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.45,0:30:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,out on the porch for a moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.05,0:30:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,listening. The cup forgotten in
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.07,0:30:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,his hand. She shouldn't have
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.89,0:30:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,noticed that. She had noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.45,0:30:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you. She said finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.61,0:30:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't. Hollis answered. But
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.91,0:30:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you will. Monday night,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.93,0:30:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,headline or resignation. The
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.56,0:30:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,hung up first. Rowina kept
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.07,0:30:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,looking at the phone for a
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.58,0:30:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,length of time
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.39,0:30:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,she couldn't measure. The
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.86,0:30:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,reflection of her own distorted
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.69,0:30:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,face on the black screen. She
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.40,0:30:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,stood up
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.87,0:30:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly. She walked to the
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.17,0:30:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,suitcase which was half open on
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.77,0:30:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,a wooden chair near the dresser.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.43,0:30:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She pulled
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.95,0:30:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,a brown file out by the rubber
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.79,0:30:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,band sat down again on the rug
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.62,0:30:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and rested the file on her own
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.46,0:30:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,thighs.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.43,0:30:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Her hands were still this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.29,0:30:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Stiller than she expected. She
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.09,0:30:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,untied the rubber band slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.47,0:30:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She opened the first flap.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.21,0:30:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Papers. Clippings of balance
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.09,0:30:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,sheets. Photocopies Hollis had
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.09,0:30:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,obtained
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.63,0:31:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,from some discreet source. Notes
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.58,0:31:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in small handwriting written by
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.46,0:31:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,herself before she met Jago
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.11,0:31:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Quint.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.99,0:31:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In a gray, noisy newsroom where
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.67,0:31:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the coffee was bad, and ambition
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.41,0:31:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,still seemed enough to
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.61,0:31:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the bills. Rowina read two lines
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.50,0:31:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,of her own field notebook and
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.21,0:31:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't recognize the woman who
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.97,0:31:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,had
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.15,0:31:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,written that. She closed the
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.74,0:31:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,file. She tied the rubber band
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.43,0:31:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,again. She put everything back
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.13,0:31:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,at the bottom
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.87,0:31:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,of the suitcase. The partner's
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.56,0:31:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,dinner was scheduled for that
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.19,0:31:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,same night.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.27,0:31:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Nieve came up in the late
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.73,0:31:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,afternoon with a dress hanging
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.48,0:31:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,from a velvet hanger. Deep wine,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.85,0:31:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,straight neckline, sleeves to
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.54,0:31:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the elbow. The fabric had a
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.12,0:31:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,specific weight to the touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.81,0:31:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That weight of something chosen
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.47,0:31:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,with attention. Rowina looked at
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.18,0:31:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,her without understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.19,0:31:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,From the master said Nieve and
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.84,0:31:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,set the hanger on the chair
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.32,0:31:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,against the wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.69,0:31:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,he asked me to leave it here. He
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.46,0:31:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,said the miss isn't obliged to
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.13,0:31:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,wear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.05,0:31:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina laughed without joy. And
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.14,0:31:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,if I don't wear it, he won't ask
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.29,0:31:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,why, said Nieve,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.81,0:31:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,with a half smile that didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.46,0:31:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,quite complete itself. But he'll
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.27,0:32:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,notice. He notices.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.95,0:32:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She wore the dress. She couldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.69,0:32:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,decide whether it was surrender
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.37,0:32:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,or courage,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.97,0:32:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and she chose not to decide. The
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.05,0:32:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,mansion's dining room had 18
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.87,0:32:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,places,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.89,0:32:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and a table that was a vanished
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.57,0:32:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,skating rink. There were six
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.08,0:32:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,partners, three wives,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.85,0:32:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Silas Ashford at one end in the
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.35,0:32:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,same gray suit as always, and
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.75,0:32:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the face of someone who has
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.05,0:32:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,already
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.39,0:32:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,seen far too much, without being
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.27,0:32:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,surprised by anything. And you
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.03,0:32:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,door a quint at the other end,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.21,0:32:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,seated as though the seat had
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.81,0:32:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,been built around her. Rowina
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.40,0:32:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,entered beside Jego. She was
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.94,0:32:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,introduced
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.49,0:32:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,by him in a sentence that left
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.47,0:32:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,no gap. Rowina Pike, she's with
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.51,0:32:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,me. It wasn't a description.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.93,0:32:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a signature. The dinner
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.61,0:32:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,advanced through courses she
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.18,0:32:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,barely tasted. There was talk
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.81,0:32:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,of an acquisition up north of a
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.65,0:32:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,land auction near the river of a
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.55,0:32:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,niece's wedding in Charleston.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.93,0:32:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina answered when addressed
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.62,0:32:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and listened when not addressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.42,0:32:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The wine was too good to be
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.93,0:32:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,wasted
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.27,0:32:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,on anxiety, so she drank slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.24,0:32:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and kept her spine straight. At
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.21,0:32:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,some point between the second
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.05,0:33:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,course and the third, Jego's
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.72,0:33:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,hand found hers on top of the
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.46,0:33:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,white table cloth. He didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.13,0:33:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,hold
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.37,0:33:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,it halfway or hide it under the
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.27,0:33:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,table. He left his hand resting
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.17,0:33:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,on top of her hand in full view
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.07,0:33:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,of
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.19,0:33:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone, and went on talking to
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.98,0:33:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,the partner to his left, as if
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.66,0:33:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the hand was some object he'd
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.29,0:33:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,found along the way, and decided
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.39,0:33:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,to keep. Silas noticed first.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.29,0:33:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina saw the small flicker in
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.33,0:33:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the lawyer's eyes, almost
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.38,0:33:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,invisible, followed by a throat
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.92,0:33:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,clearing that made way for
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.05,0:33:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing. You
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.03,0:33:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,re-arcted and take her eyes off
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.66,0:33:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,her plate, but her fork paused
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.24,0:33:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,half a second in the air,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.95,0:33:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and resumed moving with a care
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.75,0:33:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina had learned to interpret
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.61,0:33:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,as reading. You'dora read
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.11,0:33:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,people.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.97,0:33:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She did it all the time, without
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.77,0:33:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,appearing to be doing it. After
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.51,0:33:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,coffee the partner's rose
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.91,0:33:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,for cigars, and the wives went
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.94,0:33:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,off to another parlor. Rowina
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.91,0:33:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,went up alone. In the corridor
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.95,0:33:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,she
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.15,0:33:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,crossed paths with Silas, who
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.55,0:33:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,carried a folder under his arm
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.99,0:33:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and a look she couldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.10,0:33:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,decipher.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.53,0:33:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of look that holds more
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.70,0:33:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,than one interpretation, and
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.60,0:34:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,gives away none.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.27,0:34:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night, Miss. He said. Good
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.25,0:34:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,night, Mr. Ashford. He seemed to
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.30,0:34:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,want to say something more.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.27,0:34:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He weighed the moment, decided
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.83,0:34:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,against it, and went on down the
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.49,0:34:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,corridor with the firm stride of
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.15,0:34:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,someone with a set destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.95,0:34:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,In the guest room, Rowina shut
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.70,0:34:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the door and leaned against it
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.44,0:34:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,for a
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.73,0:34:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,moment. The wood was cold
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.01,0:34:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,against her back through the
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.45,0:34:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,fabric of the dress. She thought
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.09,0:34:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,about
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.35,0:34:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,tearing up the notes. She
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.70,0:34:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,thought about calling Hollis and
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.43,0:34:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,telling him the story didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.95,0:34:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.61,0:34:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She thought about telling Jago
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.99,0:34:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,everything that night, with the
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.41,0:34:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,wine still in her body and the
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.79,0:34:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,courage of exhaustion. She
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.14,0:34:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,thought about doing none of the
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.76,0:34:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,three things, and leaving it all
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.43,0:34:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,for the
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.79,0:34:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,train back. She went to the
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.48,0:34:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,bathroom, took off her makeup
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.30,0:34:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,with cold water and cotton. Put
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.24,0:34:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,on a
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.49,0:34:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,simple linen-night gown lay down
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.16,0:34:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,on top of the bed's bread, and
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.73,0:34:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,stared at the white-washed
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.08,0:34:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,ceiling
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.45,0:34:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,as the house grew quiet. Room,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.91,0:34:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,by room. She fell asleep without
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.53,0:34:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,realizing it. She was
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.25,0:34:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,welcome by the sound of the
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.74,0:34:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,door. There was no knock. The
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.34,0:34:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,door opened slowly, letting in a
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.11,0:34:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,thin
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.33,0:35:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,band of light from the corridor,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.16,0:35:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and Rowina saw against that
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.71,0:35:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,light, the silhouette of Jago
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.37,0:35:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Quint.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.25,0:35:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't turn on the room's
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.60,0:35:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,lamp. He walked to the middle of
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.14,0:35:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the room and stopped,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.65,0:35:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and only then did she notice
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.70,0:35:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,what was in his hands. The file.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.03,0:35:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Brown, no label, no rubber band
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.30,0:35:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.59,0:35:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina sat up in the bed in a
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.51,0:35:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,single motion. The air left her
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.56,0:35:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,chest in an exhalation that
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.35,0:35:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,made no sound. How...silence he
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.26,0:35:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,said without raising his voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.16,0:35:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,he saw a debt prowling this
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.82,0:35:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,corridor earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.33,0:35:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He thought it best I checked
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.17,0:35:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,before she did. His voice was
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.08,0:35:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,low. It was calm. It was empty
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.06,0:35:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,of
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.19,0:35:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,anything she could use to hold
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.85,0:35:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,on to. Jago looked at the file
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.51,0:35:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,he was carrying,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.91,0:35:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,leaped through a page she
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.19,0:35:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,recognized without needing to
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.68,0:35:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,look closely, and put the page
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.22,0:35:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,back in its
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.79,0:35:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,place, with a care that seemed
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.67,0:35:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,in that moment, the cruelest
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.42,0:35:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,thing in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.09,0:35:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Balanced sheets, he said. Copies
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.21,0:35:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,of old contracts, a list of
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.01,0:35:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,names with notes beside them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.15,0:35:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I recognized at least three of
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.75,0:35:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,the names. He lifted his eyes to
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.45,0:36:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,her. This isn't an interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.49,0:36:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't, Rowina answered,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.05,0:36:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,because denying it would have
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.79,0:36:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,been a worse insult. He nodded
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.59,0:36:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,slightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.75,0:36:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That was all. A single precise
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.69,0:36:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,nod that didn't judge, and
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.37,0:36:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore weighed more than any
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.37,0:36:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.95,0:36:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You came here for this. I came
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.85,0:36:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,here for this, she said, and I
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.76,0:36:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't know I would stop coming
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.72,0:36:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,here for
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.23,0:36:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,it. But I did stop. Weeks ago. I
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.62,0:36:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,haven't opened that file once
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.78,0:36:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,since.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.51,0:36:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Herit doesn't matter, he cut in,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.41,0:36:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and even cutting in he kept his
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.24,0:36:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,usual low tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.61,0:36:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You opened it yesterday, I heard
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.08,0:36:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you open it. I thought you were
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.50,0:36:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,closing a suitcase.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.17,0:36:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The silence settled between
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.66,0:36:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,them, with a specificity, Rowina
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.44,0:36:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn't fill,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.21,0:36:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and he didn't try to. Jago.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.88,0:36:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming to
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.31,0:36:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Savannah, he said, and that was
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.22,0:36:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.41,0:36:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,sentence that went through her
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.06,0:36:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,from side to side. Thank you for
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.83,0:36:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the weeks. The interview is paid
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.59,0:36:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,for.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.13,0:36:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If you still want it, I only ask
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.69,0:36:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that you leave tomorrow morning
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.21,0:36:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,before my mother comes down
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.53,0:36:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,for coffee. She opened her
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.15,0:36:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,mouth, closed it, opened it
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.84,0:36:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,again. Don't do this like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.41,0:37:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Like what? Without yelling at
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.23,0:37:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,me. He considered the sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.18,0:37:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He took too long to answer
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.81,0:37:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the kind of delay that is an
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.34,0:37:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,answer in itself. If I yell
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.81,0:37:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll be able to think I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.28,0:37:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,still angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.47,0:37:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,His voice found a note she had
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.14,0:37:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,never heard in him, too low to
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.81,0:37:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,have a name. I don't want you to
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.59,0:37:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,think that. I want you to leave
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.31,0:37:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,knowing exactly what stayed
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.82,0:37:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,behind. It was worse than
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.21,0:37:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,yelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.17,0:37:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It was worse than anything she
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.66,0:37:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,could have predicted that week
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.15,0:37:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,or in any week before it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.73,0:37:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago set the file on the dresser
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.36,0:37:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,near the door, with a precision
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.94,0:37:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,that seemed calculated to make
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.47,0:37:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,no noise. He didn't return it to
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.52,0:37:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,her hand. He didn't take it with
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.56,0:37:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,him. He left it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.17,0:37:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,In the middle of the way, like
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.69,0:37:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,an exposed piece of evidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.15,0:37:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,neither of them needed to
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.42,0:37:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,examine
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.77,0:37:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,anymore. Then he turned toward
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.54,0:37:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the door. Leave tomorrow. The
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.26,0:37:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,door closed behind him with the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.09,0:37:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,most
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.33,0:37:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,polite noise a door has ever
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.89,0:37:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,produced in the entire world.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.50,0:37:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena remained sitting on the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.17,0:37:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.81,0:37:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Her hands opened on the bed
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.29,0:37:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,spread. A heart beating in a
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.83,0:37:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,rhythm she didn't recognize as
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.47,0:37:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.91,0:38:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Outside in the corridor, his
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.03,0:38:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,footsteps moved away slowly. No
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.38,0:38:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,hurry, no hesitation,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.65,0:38:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and at some point between her
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.24,0:38:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,room and his room, they stopped
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.93,0:38:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,for a second before continuing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.23,0:38:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't cry. Not yet. She
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.93,0:38:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,kept looking at the file on top
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.80,0:38:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,of the dresser,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.93,0:38:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,like someone staring at an
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.26,0:38:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,animal that had followed her
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.69,0:38:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,from too far away,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.01,0:38:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to now pretend it was a
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.40,0:38:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,stranger. Outside the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.14,0:38:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the garden of the quint mansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.67,0:38:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,breathed the humid night. The
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.38,0:38:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,smell of earth and jasmine
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.92,0:38:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,rising with the breeze off the
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.70,0:38:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,river.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.47,0:38:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhere near the water, a real
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.34,0:38:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,owl called out once. Rowena
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.91,0:38:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,thought of the glass owl set
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.54,0:38:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,with red
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.01,0:38:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,stone, tucked in a dark velvet
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.76,0:38:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,box at the bottom of her bag,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.45,0:38:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and felt that this was the
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.96,0:38:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,memory
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.31,0:38:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that would hurt most on the
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.35,0:38:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,train the next day. The chapter
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.69,0:38:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,five killing the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.65,0:38:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Rain back left before eight, and
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.56,0:38:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena sat by the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.05,0:38:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,because the aisle required
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.59,0:38:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,looking at
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.19,0:38:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,people head on, and people that
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.93,0:38:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,morning would have seen what she
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.73,0:38:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,hadn't yet seen in the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.89,0:39:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She rested her forehead against
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.54,0:39:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the cold glass, and stayed that
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.20,0:39:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,way for a length of time she
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.69,0:39:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn't measure. Savannah fell
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.62,0:39:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,behind in pieces. A roof at hour
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.60,0:39:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,a line of trees bent by the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.28,0:39:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,river
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.59,0:39:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,wind, and none of it hurt with
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.56,0:39:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the noise she had expected. It
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.53,0:39:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,hurt low. It hurt the way Jago
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.49,0:39:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,had
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.69,0:39:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you in the small hours
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.41,0:39:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,when she was expecting a shout
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.25,0:39:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,anything with enough volume for
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.15,0:39:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,her
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.33,0:39:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to push back against. The file
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.00,0:39:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,was still on top of the guest
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.62,0:39:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,room dresser. She hadn't even
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.23,0:39:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,asked
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.51,0:39:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,for it back, leaving it there
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.20,0:39:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,felt fair. In the sense that
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.84,0:39:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,justice is what's left over when
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.71,0:39:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,everything else surrenders. She
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.49,0:39:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't cry on the train. She
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.10,0:39:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,counted roof panels of cars,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.27,0:39:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,counted poles, counted the times
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.98,0:39:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the conductor passed down the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.52,0:39:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,aisle dragging a coffee cart.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.07,0:39:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell of the machine coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.99,0:39:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,was cheap, and watery. Nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.85,0:39:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,like what Jago had learned to
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.64,0:39:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,make,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.23,0:39:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and that idiotic detail was what
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.05,0:39:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,came closest to breaking her.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.70,0:39:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She reached the gray city just
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.41,0:39:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,before
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.75,0:39:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,noon. The station smelled of
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.41,0:39:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,lubricant and cheap bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.94,0:39:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena carried her suitcase like
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.84,0:40:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,someone
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.25,0:40:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,carrying a witness. She cried in
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.15,0:40:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,the newsroom bathroom. It was a
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.99,0:40:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,dry cry of two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.89,0:40:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Curled up in a stall with her
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.19,0:40:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,hand over her mouth because
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.40,0:40:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Marlo Trent was on the other
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.65,0:40:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,side of the door,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.41,0:40:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,tapping the tip of her shoe and
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.25,0:40:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,speaking loudly to cover for
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.91,0:40:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,her. Come out of their
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.21,0:40:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,pike. If you stay in there any
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.72,0:40:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,longer, Hollis is going to knock
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.34,0:40:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,on the door and then I'm going
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.85,0:40:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,to have to bite him. Rowena
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.39,0:40:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,laughed in the middle of the cry
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.22,0:40:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,without meaning to. It was an
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.88,0:40:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,ugly
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.11,0:40:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,sound but it worked. She came
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.82,0:40:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,out with her face washed. Marlo
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.64,0:40:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,looked at her for a whole
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.12,0:40:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,second,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.07,0:40:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,without sarcasm for the first
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.47,0:40:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,time in years. There was
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.63,0:40:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,something different in her
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.88,0:40:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,friend's
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.27,0:40:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,expression. The shoulders
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.72,0:40:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,quieter. The way she stood still
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.57,0:40:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,without her phone in her hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.73,0:40:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay? No. Rowena answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.12,0:40:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But I will be. Marlo squeezed
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.44,0:40:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,her shoulder and her hand stayed
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.99,0:40:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,there too long for a joke. That
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.61,0:40:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,was how Rowena understood her
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.12,0:40:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,friend had guessed everything
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.64,0:40:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,before
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.95,0:40:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,asking. The newsroom had that
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.90,0:40:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,midday noise. Keys, phones
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.65,0:40:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,ringing two desks over. Someone
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.73,0:40:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,shouting
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.27,0:41:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,a page number down the hall as
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.98,0:41:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,if the whole building needed to
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.74,0:41:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,know. Hollis Vaughn lifted his
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.44,0:41:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.67,0:41:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,over his glasses the moment
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.31,0:41:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena passed down the central
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.13,0:41:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,aisle. He didn't smile. He
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.70,0:41:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't ask
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.31,0:41:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,how the trip had gone. He simply
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.13,0:41:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,pointed with his pen to the door
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.96,0:41:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,of his office. A short,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.09,0:41:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,habitual gesture. The kind that
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.03,0:41:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,allows no negotiation. She went
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.97,0:41:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,in. She shut the door behind
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.72,0:41:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,her.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.25,0:41:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That office smelled of aged
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.65,0:41:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,paper and coffee no one had the
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.25,0:41:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,courage to throw out. And there
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.85,0:41:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,was a plant in the corner that
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.62,0:41:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,had been dying for at least two
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.44,0:41:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,months. It's leaves drooping
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.09,0:41:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,over
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.33,0:41:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the edge of the pot without
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.26,0:41:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,anyone having noticed. Hollis
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.33,0:41:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,sat down his pen. He said,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.53,0:41:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,end of the day. There's not
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.23,0:41:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,going to be a headline. Hollis
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.12,0:41:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,blinked once. He leaned back in
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.07,0:41:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,his chair. Say that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.68,0:41:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not going to be a
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.23,0:41:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,headline Rowena repeated and her
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.22,0:41:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,voice
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.53,0:41:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,came out firmer than she
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.91,0:41:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,expected. I'm not going to
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.40,0:41:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,deliver what you asked for. Not
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.19,0:41:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,today,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.91,0:41:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,not next week, not ever. You
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.02,0:41:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,went there with a mission pike.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.35,0:42:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I did. And I came back without
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.60,0:42:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.83,0:42:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hollis looked at the desk for a
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.56,0:42:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,moment. When he raised his eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.34,0:42:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,there was less anger than she
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.95,0:42:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,imagined. And more a kind of old
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.80,0:42:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,disappointment, the kind of
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.36,0:42:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,disappointment boss is carry
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.98,0:42:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,from
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.21,0:42:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,other bosses before them, piled
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.13,0:42:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,up over years in rooms exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.99,0:42:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,like that one. You know what
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.72,0:42:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,this
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.97,0:42:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,means? I do. Rowena set a folded
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.15,0:42:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,paper on the desk. I'm handing
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.20,0:42:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,this over before you have to say
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.39,0:42:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.91,0:42:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hollis picked up the paper. He
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.87,0:42:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't open it. Why? He asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.84,0:42:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And the question came almost
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.67,0:42:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,gentle,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.13,0:42:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,which frightened her more than
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.81,0:42:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,an insult would have. Rowena was
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.61,0:42:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,silent for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.11,0:42:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She thought of a pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.40,0:42:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,professional answer. The kind
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.02,0:42:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,that looks good in retrospect.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.70,0:42:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,She gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.63,0:42:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the story stopped
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.08,0:42:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,existing, she said. He stopped
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.81,0:42:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,being a story. And I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.60,0:42:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,how to
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.95,0:42:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,write about someone who became a
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.64,0:42:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,person. Hollis looked at her for
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.32,0:42:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,a long time, with the expression
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.01,0:42:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,of someone re-reading an
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.43,0:42:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,equation that doesn't add up.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.14,0:42:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he nodded once, almost
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.74,0:42:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,imperceptibly.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.57,0:42:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out before I change my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.90,0:43:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He said. And Pike, she stopped
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.08,0:43:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,at the door. You were good.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.51,0:43:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena swallowed before
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.91,0:43:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,answering. I still am. Just not
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.79,0:43:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,for this. She shut the door
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.42,0:43:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.75,0:43:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hollis was leaning against the
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.42,0:43:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,corridor wall, waiting with two
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.14,0:43:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,cups of machine coffee. And she
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.87,0:43:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,pushed one of the cups into
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.34,0:43:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena's hand without ceremony,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.02,0:43:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,like someone handing over a
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.49,0:43:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,survival item.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.25,0:43:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you do it? She asked. I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.04,0:43:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit. Marlo blew on the coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.37,0:43:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the club of the
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.12,0:43:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,dignified unemployed. Rowena
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.01,0:43:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,laughed. It was a short broken
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.03,0:43:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,laugh,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.69,0:43:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but it was a laugh. They went
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.33,0:43:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,down the stairs instead of the
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.02,0:43:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,elevator. On the sidewalk,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.07,0:43:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the city was grey the way it had
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.70,0:43:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,always been. And Rowena looked
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.23,0:43:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,at the buildings without any of
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.82,0:43:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.97,0:43:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,glow that Savannah painted onto
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.86,0:43:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,even a cloudy morning. Something
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.82,0:43:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,was missing from that sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.41,0:43:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell of Magnollia was
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.00,0:43:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,missing. The way the Savannah
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.77,0:43:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,river appeared between two
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.36,0:43:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,streets
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.79,0:43:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,when no one expected it. A strip
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.70,0:43:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,of lead-coloured water that
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.31,0:44:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,somehow made everything lighter
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.15,0:44:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,was missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.31,0:44:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,E was missing. You're going
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.42,0:44:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,back, Marlo said, without
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.37,0:44:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,asking. I am. Will he take you
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.72,0:44:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,back?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.53,0:44:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. He will. Marlo
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.13,0:44:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,insisted looking off into the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.79,0:44:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.95,0:44:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A man who sends for you three
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.79,0:44:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,weeks in a row doesn't close a
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.70,0:44:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,door for good. He locks it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.41,0:44:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's different. Rowena looked at
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.44,0:44:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,her friend, and for an instant,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.40,0:44:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the world stopped spinning so
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.23,0:44:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.13,0:44:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Marlo. What? Thank you. Get out
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.61,0:44:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,of here before I cry, Pike. It
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.01,0:44:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't suit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.77,0:44:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena took the night train and
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.50,0:44:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,slept enough not to look
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.84,0:44:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,devastated on arrival. The car
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.51,0:44:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,smelled of old fabric and rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.14,0:44:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and she kept her face turned to
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.77,0:44:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the dark window for much of the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.41,0:44:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.95,0:44:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,watching her own reflection
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.50,0:44:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,without being able to look away.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.34,0:44:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,On Sunday morning, Savannah
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.89,0:44:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,received
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.35,0:44:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,a train with the sun coming in
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.95,0:44:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,from the side, and the whole
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.44,0:44:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,station smelled of bakery and
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.98,0:44:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,river
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.25,0:44:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,breeze. She took a taxi without
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.13,0:44:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,stopping to think. She went in
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.95,0:44:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,through the front. She rang the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.83,0:44:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.57,0:45:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Feeling answered. His eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.07,0:45:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,widened for half a second,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.57,0:45:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,before returning to normal
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.07,0:45:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,trained.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.09,0:45:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Pike. I need to talk to
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.97,0:45:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,him. He's in his office with
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.84,0:45:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,guests. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.31,0:45:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Feeling hesitated. Then he
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.95,0:45:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,stepped aside. Miss is quint
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.72,0:45:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,arrived in our ego. He said
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.42,0:45:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.93,0:45:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost a warning. And Miss
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.82,0:45:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Martian came along. Rowena
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.72,0:45:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,nodded. Druid deep breath once
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.90,0:45:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and walk down
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.85,0:45:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the marble corridor. Like
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.27,0:45:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,someone walking to a trial she
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.98,0:45:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,herself had scheduled. The
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.47,0:45:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,corridor was
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.15,0:45:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,silent except for her own
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.48,0:45:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,footsteps, and their echo on the
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.19,0:45:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,old tiles sounded too firm for
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.78,0:45:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,the way she
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.37,0:45:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,was feeling inside. J. goes
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.97,0:45:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,office was in the west wing of
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.75,0:45:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the mansion, and the door was a
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.59,0:45:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,jar.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.27,0:45:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She heard before she saw the
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.23,0:45:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,voice of Odeck Martian. Sweet,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.33,0:45:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,too loud. That voice of someone
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.50,0:45:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,who
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.71,0:45:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,tends to console and measures
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.88,0:45:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the effect in a mirror. A
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.76,0:45:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,necessary evil Eudora. Truly,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.53,0:45:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,better to find out now than
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.18,0:45:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena opened the door before a
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.08,0:45:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,debt finished. The entire office
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.04,0:45:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,went
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.29,0:45:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,still. J. goes stood behind the
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.23,0:46:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,desk, dark jacket hands resting
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.16,0:46:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,on the top. Eudora seated in the
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.16,0:46:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,green
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.47,0:46:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,velvet armchair near the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.30,0:46:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,back straight as ever, as if her
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.13,0:46:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,posture were the last line of
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.49,0:46:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,silence leaning against the
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.21,0:46:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,bookcase. Neutral expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.06,0:46:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Eyes that recognized Rowena
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.79,0:46:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,before
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.17,0:46:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the rest of his body did. Odeck
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.26,0:46:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,on the sofa. Glass in hand. A
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.21,0:46:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,smile dressing her mouth until
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.23,0:46:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,it froze when she saw who had
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.16,0:46:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,come in. J. go didn't move. Only
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.28,0:46:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,his jaw tenced once.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.17,0:46:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena. Said silence almost
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.95,0:46:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically. Trying to smooth
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.00,0:46:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,things over. Stay, Rowena asked
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.05,0:46:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,without taking her eyes off J.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.21,0:46:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,go. All of you. Stay. Odeck
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.15,0:46:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,opened her mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.87,0:46:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena gave her no chance. I
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.79,0:46:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,came to tell the truth. She
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.64,0:46:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,said. All of it. I'm not going
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.69,0:46:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,to
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.83,0:46:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,apologize first because an
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.48,0:46:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,apology before the truth is an
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.39,0:46:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,insult. Eudora raised an
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.92,0:46:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,eyebrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.79,0:46:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing more. Rowena breathed.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.74,0:46:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Her voice came out firm, even
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.63,0:46:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,though her hands trembled inside
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.71,0:46:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,her jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.87,0:46:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to Savannah with two
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.42,0:47:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,missions. The interview was one.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.25,0:47:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The other was to come back with
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.03,0:47:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,material that would destroy the
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.87,0:47:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Quint family. My editor wanted a
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.77,0:47:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,scandal story and I accepted
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.43,0:47:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,because I needed the job. I
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.03,0:47:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,accepted believing I could
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.58,0:47:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,separate the work from the
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.12,0:47:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,charade. She paused.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.85,0:47:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't. Odeck let out a low
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.00,0:47:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,incredulous laugh. No one joined
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.21,0:47:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,her. I brought the file.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.33,0:47:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena continued and her voice
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.11,0:47:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't waver. You already know I
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.01,0:47:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,brought it. It was found.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.97,0:47:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It was red. And it was returned
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.63,0:47:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,in the small hours of yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.29,0:47:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,morning with a thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.57,0:47:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,that hurt more than any shout
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.31,0:47:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,would have. She looked at Jego.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.17,0:47:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't look away. He didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.97,0:47:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,confirm. His face was that of a
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.91,0:47:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,man counting every word before
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.79,0:47:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,deciding what to do with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.93,0:47:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I could have gone back to the
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.66,0:47:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,newsroom, written what my editor
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.58,0:47:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,wanted, saved my career.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.55,0:47:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A voice rose half a tone. I
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.29,0:47:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't write it. I killed the
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.17,0:47:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,story this morning. I resigned
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.10,0:47:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,before
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.49,0:47:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,he could fire me. There's no
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.18,0:47:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,story anymore. There's no file
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.98,0:47:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,anymore. There's nothing left in
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.91,0:48:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,that guest room that's of use to
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.74,0:48:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,anyone. She took a step forward
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.52,0:48:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,just one. And I didn't come here
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.35,0:48:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,for forgiveness. I came because
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.89,0:48:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,if I didn't say this in front of
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.49,0:48:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone who watched the lie
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.88,0:48:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.77,0:48:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the truth would remain a private
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.72,0:48:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,thing and the lie was public.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.49,0:48:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.97,0:48:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Total silence. You'd aura
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.64,0:48:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,blinked once. Slowly. Like
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.38,0:48:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,someone recalculating something
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.45,0:48:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,she thought was
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.45,0:48:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,settled. Odeck looked at her
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.19,0:48:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,glasses if it had betrayed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.11,0:48:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I dropped the story. Rowena said
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.09,0:48:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and her voice lowered again.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.06,0:48:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost soft. Because he stopped
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.23,0:48:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,being the story. I couldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.13,0:48:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,write about a man who learned my
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.84,0:48:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,coffee by heart. She finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.44,0:48:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Her hands were still trembling.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.65,0:48:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She let them tremble. Odeck rose
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.58,0:48:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,first. Her glass coming down
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.26,0:48:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,hard on the side tray.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.95,0:48:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What a spectacle. She said.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.64,0:48:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeking Jago's eyes. You're not
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.59,0:48:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,going to believe this are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.97,0:48:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago didn't answer Odeck. He
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.53,0:48:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,looked at Rowena for a length of
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.30,0:48:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,time no one there could count.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.97,0:48:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he pulled back his chair,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.50,0:49:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,unhurried and stood up. Jago.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.99,0:49:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapter 6 His laugh. He go cross
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.46,0:49:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the office in a single stride.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.77,0:49:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't seem like a stride.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.20,0:49:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed like decision walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.82,0:49:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena didn't step back but she
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.38,0:49:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,held her breath in the middle of
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.00,0:49:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,her chest as if her body had
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.69,0:49:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,forgotten how to do it. He
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.25,0:49:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,stopped half a meter from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.06,0:49:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.60,0:49:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,touch her. He just stood there.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.57,0:49:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,His eyes fixed on her and there
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.53,0:49:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,was something in that gaze
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.18,0:49:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.56,0:49:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn't name. Neither anger nor
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.66,0:49:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,relief. Something that made her
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.70,0:49:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,hold her own breath. Odeck.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.76,0:49:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He said without looking back.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.46,0:49:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my house. The silence
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.33,0:49:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,in the room had weight. The kind
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.20,0:49:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,of
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.32,0:49:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,silence that makes people hold
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.36,0:49:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,their breath without realizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.46,0:49:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago. Now, his voice came out
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.43,0:49:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,low,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.10,0:49:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,courteous. The way he spoke to
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.04,0:49:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone. And even so, no one in
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.10,0:49:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the room had any doubt. Odeck
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.97,0:49:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,picked
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.36,0:49:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,up her bag with rigid movements
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.87,0:49:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,her fingers gripping the
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.03,0:49:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,leather. She didn't look at you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.54,0:49:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,dora.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.78,0:49:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The door slammed behind her with
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.73,0:49:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the thin noise of high heels
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.43,0:49:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that had lost their audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.78,0:50:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago breathed once. Then he
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.39,0:50:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,looked at Rowena as if he were
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.17,0:50:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,checking a calculation that had
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.02,0:50:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,taken far too long to add up. I
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.02,0:50:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,want you to hear this. He said,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.02,0:50:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,loud enough for siless and
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.70,0:50:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,utora to hear every word and
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.33,0:50:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,loud enough to carry through the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.18,0:50:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,open door and reach the corridor
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.04,0:50:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,where half a dozen of you dora's
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.28,0:50:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,guests pretended not to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.45,0:50:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She stays with me. And tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.62,0:50:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,all of Savannah will hear it
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.31,0:50:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,from my mouth before hearing it
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.19,0:50:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,from anyone else's. He paused
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.94,0:50:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,for an instant, as if the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.40,0:50:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,sentence carried weight. I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.04,0:50:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,done letting fear choose for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.91,0:50:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He raised his hand
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.96,0:50:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly. He touched the tips of
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.64,0:50:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,his fingers to her chin. The
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.21,0:50:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,touch as light as a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.54,0:50:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay. Rowena felt her eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.37,0:50:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,sting. She didn't look away.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.35,0:50:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stay. Silas let out the air
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.61,0:50:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,he'd been
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.24,0:50:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,holding. Udora didn't move. But
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.94,0:50:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,something in the line of her
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.47,0:50:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulders gave way a millimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.22,0:50:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the matriarch who broke
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.00,0:50:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the silence at last, with that
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.78,0:50:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,voice that never missed its
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.38,0:50:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,tone even on hard days. Out of
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.27,0:50:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,here she said, addressing
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.84,0:51:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,neither of them in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.72,0:51:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All of
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.10,0:51:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you I need to think. Rowena and
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.97,0:51:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago left together. Silas closed
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.91,0:51:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the door with the care of
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.42,0:51:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,someone
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.84,0:51:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,who knows that a well-closed
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.72,0:51:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,door is sometimes worth an
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.46,0:51:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,entire contract. In the corridor
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.61,0:51:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.88,0:51:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,held Rowena's hand. That was
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.97,0:51:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,all. He didn't kiss her. He
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.99,0:51:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't speak. He just held it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.24,0:51:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,His fingers
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.06,0:51:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,laced through hers with a quiet
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.04,0:51:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,firmness, unlike anything she'd
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.01,0:51:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,known in him until then. He let
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.99,0:51:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,her
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.18,0:51:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,out onto the back porch, the one
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.35,0:51:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,facing the Savannah river. The
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.38,0:51:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,late afternoon sun fell golden
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.41,0:51:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,on the
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.82,0:51:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,water, tinting the surface
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.29,0:51:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,copper and amber, and the smell
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.05,0:51:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,of the garden came heavy with
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.69,0:51:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Magnolia wet from the night
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.41,0:51:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,before. Somewhere in the middle
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.38,0:51:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,of the garden an insect sang the
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.41,0:51:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,same repeated note, rhythmic in
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.67,0:51:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,no hurry. You killed the story,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.92,0:51:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,said Jago, looking at the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.71,0:51:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a question. I did. You
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.14,0:51:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,lost your job. I did. He turned
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.48,0:51:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,his head slowly, and his profile
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.91,0:52:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,against the late afternoon light
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.61,0:52:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,had a hardness Rowena couldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.19,0:52:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,read in full. She could only
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.68,0:52:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,read
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.89,0:52:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the part that mattered. I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.57,0:52:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,going to help you find another
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.44,0:52:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,one. He said, one you choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.25,0:52:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Not one
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.69,0:52:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I choose for you. Rowena laughed
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.84,0:52:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,softly. The laugh came out
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.58,0:52:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,choked. A little crooked. The
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.53,0:52:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,way
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.73,0:52:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,laughs happen when the body
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.36,0:52:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't quite know yet, whether
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.22,0:52:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,it's crying or smiling. You said
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.15,0:52:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,choose and for you. In the same
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.34,0:52:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,sentence, Quint. Careful. He
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.32,0:52:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,closed his eyes for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.37,0:52:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,When he
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.87,0:52:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,opened them, his shoulders had
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.59,0:52:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,dropped half a finger, and his
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.32,0:52:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,mouth gave way in a near smile
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.04,0:52:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.39,0:52:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,had never seen there. I'll
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.24,0:52:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,learn. It was there behind them
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.45,0:52:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that the porch door opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.95,0:52:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yudora came out without
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.25,0:52:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,announcing herself. She didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.94,0:52:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,look at Jago first. She looked
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.63,0:52:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,at Rowena,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.67,0:52:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and there was in that gaze and a
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.30,0:52:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,praisele different from the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.68,0:52:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,earlier ones without the usual
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.21,0:52:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,scalpel. The matriarch crossed
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.16,0:52:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the stone floor, and stopped in
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.18,0:52:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,front of her. Up close in the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.07,0:52:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,low
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.27,0:52:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,rosy light of that afternoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.01,0:52:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yudora seemed smaller than on
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.75,0:53:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the night of the ball. Smaller
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.55,0:53:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and older
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.09,0:53:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and less sharp, as if she'd left
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.16,0:53:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,her armor hanging on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.23,0:53:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena waited for the
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.59,0:53:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,blow that didn't come. Yudora
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.42,0:53:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,extended her hand. She touched
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.31,0:53:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena's arm lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.17,0:53:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The thumb sliding once over the
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.70,0:53:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,sleeve of the jacket. A gesture
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.24,0:53:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,so restrained it could have
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.57,0:53:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,gone unnoticed, but it didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.26,0:53:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Then she turned her head and
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.84,0:53:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,looked into the hall. The wide
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.54,0:53:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,door was
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.99,0:53:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,open. And from there you could
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.51,0:53:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,see the empty chair. The one
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.92,0:53:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,that had always been near the
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.39,0:53:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,window
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.69,0:53:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,of the main hall, its back
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.17,0:53:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,turned slightly to the side, as
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.93,0:53:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,if someone had just stood up and
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.75,0:53:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,would come back at any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.28,0:53:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yudora kept looking long enough
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.87,0:53:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,for the moment to grow heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.85,0:53:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You have his laugh, she
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.21,0:53:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,murmured. Rowena didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.57,0:53:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,understand. She felt her heart
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.34,0:53:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,skipped a whole
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.23,0:53:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,beat, but she didn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.24,0:53:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yudora didn't explain. She just
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.19,0:53:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,squeezed her arm once very
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.83,0:53:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,lightly,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.81,0:53:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and went back inside. The door
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.45,0:53:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,closed behind her without a
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.93,0:53:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,sound, as if the house were
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.40,0:53:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,protecting
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.95,0:53:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that secret too. Rowena looked
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.11,0:53:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,at Jago. His jaw was locked. His
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.42,0:54:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,gaze fixed on some point of the
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.65,0:54:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,river that no longer belonged to
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.12,0:54:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that afternoon. Jago. Later, he
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.50,0:54:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,said quietly. Please, she didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.97,0:54:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,insist. She stored the question
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.65,0:54:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,in the same place where she
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.12,0:54:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,stored all the details that
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.58,0:54:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.91,0:54:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,yet have a frame. She kept
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.49,0:54:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,storing, because that was what
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.32,0:54:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,she knew how to do. And because
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.21,0:54:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,not
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.39,0:54:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,every detail asked to be opened
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.07,0:54:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,on the same day it appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.59,0:54:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yudora back inside at the end of
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.33,0:54:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.49,0:54:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,afternoon. When the river was
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.07,0:54:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,already dark blue, and the
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.49,0:54:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,mansions lights were beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.13,0:54:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to come on one
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.89,0:54:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,by one, as if the house were
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.87,0:54:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,breathing. They ate little. No
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.99,0:54:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,one spoke much. Silas passed
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.96,0:54:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,down the
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.53,0:54:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,corridor once, nodded agreeding,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.35,0:54:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and vanished off toward the
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.89,0:54:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,library. Nieve brought tea
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.38,0:54:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,without asking,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.67,0:54:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and disappeared before anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.24,0:54:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,could thank her. Then it was
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.75,0:54:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago who extended his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.67,0:54:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena accepted. They went up
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.40,0:54:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the main staircase together. Her
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.32,0:54:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,footsteps echoed on the marble.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.17,0:54:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,His almost didn't. He always
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.94,0:54:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,stepped as if he didn't want to
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.89,0:54:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,take up more space than
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.34,0:54:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.55,0:55:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Halfway up the stairs he
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.90,0:55:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,stopped. He turned her slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.59,0:55:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,His hand played against the
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.11,0:55:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,nape of her neck, and pressed
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.48,0:55:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,his forehead to hers for a
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.70,0:55:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,length of time that belonged to
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.17,0:55:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,no clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.99,0:55:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to do this
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.68,0:55:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,right. He said, too low to be
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.50,0:55:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,anything but honest. No one
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.20,0:55:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,does.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.91,0:55:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He laughed. It was a short laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.69,0:55:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,almost startled. The kind of
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.24,0:55:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,laugh that escapes before a
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.74,0:55:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,person
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.07,0:55:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,decides to let it out. Rowena
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.70,0:55:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,stored that laugh, too. She
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.21,0:55:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,stored it the same way she
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.67,0:55:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,stored
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.01,0:55:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,everything that mattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.60,0:55:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Without noting it down, without
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.57,0:55:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,recording it. Just letting it
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.41,0:55:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,settle deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.59,0:55:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They kept going up. At the top
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.31,0:55:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the corridor had that late night
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.14,0:55:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,mansion silence that isn't
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.63,0:55:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the silence of emptiness. It's
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.60,0:55:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the silence of care. The door to
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.69,0:55:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,his room was a jar. He pushed it
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.79,0:55:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,with the back of his hand. A
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.56,0:55:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,casual gesture that contained a
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.51,0:55:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,whole decision. She went in. He
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.47,0:55:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,went in
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.91,0:55:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,behind her. The door closed
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.81,0:55:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly. The kitchen. The next
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.85,0:55:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,morning. Smelled of coffee and
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.96,0:55:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,warm bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.23,0:55:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The Savannah light came in from
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.81,0:55:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the side through the high
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.08,0:56:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,window, cut into bands by the
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.55,0:56:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,frames,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.43,0:56:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and fell gold and over the white
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.29,0:56:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,tablecloth, over the cups, over
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.10,0:56:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the still warm loaves that
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.61,0:56:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,neither had left in a basket,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.12,0:56:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and disappeared before anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.64,0:56:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,could thank her. That was how
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.15,0:56:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,neither did things. Before hand
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.68,0:56:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and without making noise. Rowena
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.28,0:56:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,sat with her legs crossed in the
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.89,0:56:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,bag. Jago sat beside her. So
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.72,0:56:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,close that his knee touched hers
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.80,0:56:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,under the table. He didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.50,0:56:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.29,0:56:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He just extended his hand over
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.12,0:56:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the white tablecloth and waited.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.06,0:56:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena placed hers on top. They
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.95,0:56:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,stayed that way. Unhurried.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.54,0:56:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,While the heat of the coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.18,0:56:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,rose in a thread of steam
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.65,0:56:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.59,0:56:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She looked at the cup. He had
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.30,0:56:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,made the coffee the way she
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.90,0:56:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,liked it. Two dashes of sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.67,0:56:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,More
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.91,0:56:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,milk than any barista would
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.55,0:56:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,accept. He'd made it without
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.25,0:56:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,asking. She smiled into the cup
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.12,0:56:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and said
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.61,0:56:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing. Because she didn't need
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.29,0:56:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,to. From the other side of the
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.87,0:56:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,kitchen,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.69,0:56:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,through the arch doorway you
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.96,0:56:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,could see the corner of the main
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.41,0:56:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,hall. And from there you could
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.77,0:56:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,see the
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.09,0:56:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,empty chair near the window. Its
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.91,0:56:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,back was still turned slightly
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.61,0:57:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,to the side, as it had been the
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.37,0:57:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,afternoon before. As on every
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.12,0:57:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,morning Rowena had spent in that
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.06,0:57:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,house. No one had moved the
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.69,0:57:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,chair
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.99,0:57:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,during the night. No one had
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.68,0:57:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,occupied it as far as she knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.55,0:57:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,On any of the times she'd been
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.37,0:57:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,there.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.73,0:57:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A laugh. Someone you'dora had
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.82,0:57:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,known. Someone Jago had known. A
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.12,0:57:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,name the house had decided to
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.20,0:57:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,stop
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.49,0:57:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,saying, guarded with such care
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.37,0:57:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that even the silence around it
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.32,0:57:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,had shaped. Rowena opened her
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.13,0:57:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.95,0:57:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago. He lifted his eyes from
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.02,0:57:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the coffee. He didn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.08,0:57:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, she said,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.87,0:57:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and her voice came out soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.54,0:57:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrated. So as not to break
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.33,0:57:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that morning. Your mother said
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.11,0:57:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,something.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.71,0:57:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,About a laugh. Jago's hand
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.76,0:57:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,overhears tightened a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.05,0:57:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That was all. A small,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.91,0:57:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,involuntary squeeze the kind
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.56,0:57:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that happens before a person
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.21,0:57:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,decides to do it. Boo! She
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.74,0:57:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.05,0:57:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Not because he interrupted her
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.70,0:57:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,with any word. It was the
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.08,0:57:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,silence that did the work. A
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.62,0:57:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,whole
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.89,0:57:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,round silence that filled the
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.51,0:57:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,table and the coffee and the
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.06,0:57:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,savanna light falling between
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.68,0:58:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,them as
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.07,0:58:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,if the sun too were waiting. He
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.53,0:58:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,looked at the cup. Then at her
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.91,0:58:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,hand under his hand. Then for a
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.37,0:58:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,tea chair far off golden in the
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.28,0:58:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,morning. He didn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.88,0:58:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena felt then with a cold and
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.85,0:58:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,new certainty that there was an
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.78,0:58:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,entire story living inside that
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.70,0:58:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,house, not in the walls or the
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.57,0:58:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,old furniture, but in the people
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.27,0:58:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,who lived in it and carried it
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.87,0:58:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,without saying the name. She had
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.58,0:58:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,just
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.79,0:58:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,knocked on the right door. The
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.39,0:58:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,door was not going to open that
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.05,0:58:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,morning. She stored the question
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.76,0:58:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,in
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.87,0:58:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,her throat. The way she had
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.40,0:58:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,always stored what didn't yet
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.04,0:58:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,have its time. She closed her
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.68,0:58:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,hand
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.91,0:58:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,around his. Outside a bird sang
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.99,0:58:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,a high note and flew away. The
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.00,0:58:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,empty chair remained empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.39,0:58:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Golden in the sun occupying the
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.07,0:58:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,place it had always occupied and
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.81,0:58:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,she understood without anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.39,0:58:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,needing to say it. That that
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.98,0:58:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,morning of peace was only the
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.62,0:58:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,beginning of something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.84,0:59:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,months later, she woke up every
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.70,0:59:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,day in Jago's arms. In the
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.10,0:59:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,two of them. Slow kisses,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.04,0:59:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,whispered promises, his body
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.22,0:59:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,fitted to hers as if the world
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.55,0:59:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,outside didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.64,0:59:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,exist. Until the bodyguard
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.43,0:59:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,started following her into the
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.50,0:59:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,more bathroom. Until he deleted
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.63,0:59:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.84,0:59:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,job offer that had come for her
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.71,0:59:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,without saying a word. Until the
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.63,0:59:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,phone rang and a name, a name
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.38,0:59:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,no one in that family dare to
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.39,0:59:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,speak. May Jago go pale. Hang up
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.62,0:59:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,mid sentence. And lie with his
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.70,0:59:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.98,0:59:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,still glazed with dread. She saw
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.29,0:59:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the raw fear there. The same
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.31,0:59:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,fear he had been hiding since
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.40,0:59:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the night they kissed for the
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.14,0:59:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,first time, pretending it was
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.88,0:59:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,only a game. The old secret
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.50,0:59:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,between
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.92,0:59:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,them was no longer a shadow. It
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.91,0:59:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,was an open wound. Capable of
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.77,0:59:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,explaining the controlling man
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.70,0:59:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago had become and of
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.04,0:59:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,destroying forever the man she
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.87,0:59:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,had loved. Now she trembled
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.51,0:59:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,alone in the
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.24,1:00:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,luxurious bedroom, tasting the
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.04,1:00:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,bitter flavor of betrayed trust.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.96,1:00:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And what if the past he had
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.58,1:00:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,locked away
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.24,1:00:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,with guilt was greater than the
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.17,1:00:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,love he swore he felt. And what
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.10,1:00:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,if opening that door made him
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.91,1:00:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,hate
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.16,1:00:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,her forever? And what if the
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.70,1:00:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,beautiful golden cage was the
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.29,1:00:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,only thing still keeping the two
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.05,1:00:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,of
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.16,1:00:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,them together? Like I said, that